        <div class="layer-section-heading">
          <h2>Application-Specific Stackup Recommendations</h2>
          <p>Every 20-layer design has different signal-integrity, power-delivery, and cost requirements. Our recommended starting points are based on hundreds of successful 20-layer builds.</p>
        </div>

